ygData.messageBody:
Hiya!

Rodcet Nife had the most active guild from the list, Mystic Alliance. We
just had a fun event last night fighting sand giants (higher-ups) and madmen
(lower lvl) and pumas (REALLY low) it was really fun :) If your interested
in joining the Mystic Alliance, just give a tell in-game to Fentus,
Genesius, Damarr, Taren, Kerik, or Jaleth!

-joe
Fentus Fayspark
Rodcet Nife
